(181, 1, '2019-10-14 07:56:25', '2019-10-14 07:56:25', '', 'FBL-EUR-C1-TOTTENHAM-BAYERN MUNICH', 'Bayern Munich\'s German midfielder Serge Gnabry (C) celebrates after scoring their third goal during the UEFA Champions League Group B football match between Tottenham Hotspur and Bayern Munich at the Tottenham Hotspur Stadium in north London, on October 1, 2019. (Photo by DANIEL LEAL-OLIVAS / AFP)        (Photo credit should read DANIEL LEAL-OLIVAS/AFP/Getty Images)', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'fbl-eur-c1-tottenham-bayern-munich', '', '', '2019-10-14 07:56:25', '2019-10-14 07:56:25', '', 178, 'http://localhost/seagamefootball/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/53.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0);
